      <section eId="sec_44_2_131">
        <num>44-2-131</num>
        <content>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1917, p. 108, § 45; Code 1933, § 60-409; Ga. L. 1998, p. 128, § 44; Ga. L. 2011, p. 752, § 44/HB 142; Ga. L. 2019, p. 1056, § 44/SB 52.)</p>
          <p>The 2011 amendment,
      effective May 13, 2011, part of an Act to revise, modernize, and correct the Code, substituted "former Code Section 53-4-2 as such existed on December 31, 1997, if applicable, or Code Sections 53-1-7 and 53-2-1," for "Code Section 53-4-2 of the 'Pre-1998 Probate Code,' if applicable, or Code Sections 53-1-7 and 53-2-1 of the 'Revised Probate Code of 1998,'" in subsection (i).</p>
          <p>The 2019 amendment,
      effective May 12, 2019, part of an Act to revise, modernize, and correct the Code, inserted "that" following "provided, however," in subsection (d).</p>
        </content>
      </section>
